Space Hulk: Deathwing - a game in the genre of first-person shooter (FPS), based on the classic board game Space Hulk from Games Workshop. The game takes place in the universe of Warhammer 40000. Project Space Hulk: Deathwing is developed on the technology of Unreal Engine 4 and gives you a chance to enter into a fierce battle with the Genacrands in the narrow corridors of the Space Wanderer in the company of three friends. Getting experience in missions, you develop skills and master skills, and get new equipment.
